## ✅ যেগুলো ভালো করা হয়েছে (Strengths)

| Feature | Assessment |
|---------|------------|
| Enum types for all statuses | ✅ Excellent — prevents typo-based data corruption |
| `set_updated_at()` triggers on all tables | ✅ Consistent `updated_at` management |
| Application stage transition validation | ✅ Solid state machine with `before_update_applications()` |
| Optimistic concurrency (`version` column) | ✅ Great for multi-user race condition prevention |
| `citext` for emails | ✅ Case-insensitive email matching |
| `applications_unique_job_candidate` constraint | ✅ Prevents duplicate applications |
| Resume deduplication via `file_hash` partial index | ✅ Smart approach |
| Bootstrap trigger idempotency (`IF NOT EXISTS`) | ✅ Safe to re-run |
| `block_non_admin_profile_privilege_changes` | ✅ Good security guard |
| Comprehensive GIN indexes for skills/arrays | ✅ Good query performance planning |

---

## 🎯 Priority Fix Order

1. **🔴 RLS Policies on all tables** — Do this BEFORE any real user data enters the system
2. **🔴 Drop `password_hash` and `auth_sessions`** — Remove dead code
3. **🟠 Add role enforcement on `recruiter_id` FKs** — Prevent data corruption
4. **🟠 Fix `moved_by` in stage history trigger** — Critical for audit compliance
5. **🟠 Add `scoring_config` validation** — Prevent broken scoring
6. **🟡 Fix remaining MEDIUM issues** — Before beta launch
7. **🔵 Address LOW issues** — Can be done incrementally
